00:47:07.920 --> 00:47:11.640
the popularization of
say making science--

00:47:11.640 --> 00:47:16.970
giving access to science for all
of the North Korean population,

00:47:16.970 --> 00:47:20.330
along with quickly eradicating
illiteracy and getting kids

00:47:20.330 --> 00:47:23.830
into schools was
really, really important.

