of these tour groups.

00:58:59.890 --> 00:59:03.370
And he has recently sent me
this fantastic collection

00:59:03.370 --> 00:59:07.750
of postcards from the science--
There's a science center,

00:59:07.750 --> 00:59:10.590
like a science world or
whatever in Pyongyang

00:59:10.590 --> 00:59:13.350
that is delightful and colorful.

00:59:13.350 --> 00:59:16.800
And so, my sense is that
scientific education

00:59:16.800 --> 00:59:19.760
and [inaudible] science and
STEM is as important now

00:59:19.760 --> 00:59:21.220
in North Korea as
it has ever been.

